headline: GTA Online
subtitle: 2X GTA$ and RP on The High Society Leak Finale
content:
One of the leads on Dr. Dre’s stolen tracks points straight to a mansion party in Rockford Hills. You’ll be dressed the part, play it cool to enter the party and track down the source, then coordinate with Franklin and Imani on the extraction.

Operators will earn 2X GTA$ and RP on The High Society Leak Finale, which features Dr. Dre’s track The Scenic Route, all week long.
